items.badge_description: It takes the perfect amount of light, the right framing and a touch of creative love to get the perfect picture of your brew. Now it’s time to drink it! That’s 110 check-ins with a photo.
Normally DIY furniture and meatballs are all that come to mind, but now you can add Swedish beer to that list! That's 50 different beers from a brewery from Sweden. Try 5 more for Level 11.

While spontaneity can be fun, sometimes you want to make sure your adventure will rock. Checkout the menu at an Untappd Verified Venue before visiting and know exactly what’s on tap! That's 455 check-ins at venue that is verified.  Try 5 more for Level 92!
Traveling the world is hard, but not for you. It's as easy as cracking open a new brew! You have had a beer from at least 5 different regions around the world. Try 5 more for Level 2!

It's time to give bottle shops some love by adding them as your purchased location. That's 195 check-ins with a purchased location! Tag 5 more to get to Level 40. Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 65 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 14!
Normally DIY furniture and meatballs are all that come to mind, but now you can add Swedish beer to that list! That's 70 different beers from a brewery from Sweden. Try 5 more Level 15.

Canning is all the rage and it's not hard to see why - travels well, more environmentally friendly, and no need to carry your bottle opener. That's 100 checkins with the serving style of Can. Try 5 more for Level 21! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast
